channel.title: What's the latest in 0x00sec?
channel.description:
Let's just say I have been away for a while. Been working on my pretty obvious personal site so I had to cancel a few of my 0x00sec projects since anyone would be able to compare it with my current one (Or accuse me of plagiarism :p)
I've met up with a new partner in crime and have taken another person under my wing to show them what I know.
Hope to meet all the newcomers and see the old ones again soon :)
